Invocation Name: charlottesville city guide
des: This app is for visitors who are making a trip to visit the beautiful city of Charlottesville Virginia. Explore the riches of the city by finding landmarks and attractions that are unique to this college city and this app will provide contact details if users require more information. Use this app to get a head start in preparing a trip to one of the most relaxing and gorgeous cities in the United States.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
